<br>
As to what is most efficient when you solo;<br>
<br>
It doesnt really help if you can blast a mob down quite fast, if you need to med for 3 minutes afterwards :-) Much better to take weaker mobs that you can more or less take down nonstop.<br>
<br>
As to earth or not, the faster mob dies (fire for example), the less damage your pet takes. And the faster it regens to max.<br>
<br>
While water regens faster generally, so it can allow some more damage taken.<br>
<br>
I guess the root adds some safety, but then you stop the mob from fleeing (bad/good thing) and you have to do the 15% extra damage per mob. I dont like that.<br>
